; ADR-0072 patch (1) = comat routine chip_type guard + PMDDOTNET inline voice table load verify
; PMDDotNET emits @N as 0xFF N + voice definition as inline voice table (= [voice_num][25 byte data]...[0x00 0xFF] terminator)
; Driver currently looks up voice_table[N] from compile.py separate label table; PMDDOTNET path needs inline voice loader
;
; This fixture exercises @001 voice change on each FM part with simple notes
; Expected: voice 1 register data loaded to FM 0x30-0x9F + 0xB0 area per part

; FM voice 1 (= simple alg 0 fbl 0)
; nm alg fbl
